1 Go to Download section
2 download the org-cakephp-codetemplate.nbm file
3 open your netbeans
4 Go to options Tools menu then plug-ins
5 In the new window go to Downloaded tab
6 Select the *.nbm you've just download
7 install it

New code templates added from http://cakephpcheatsheet.com thanks to Wessel Strengholt

Based on the work of evilbloodydemon
Check the original project here : 
https://github.com/evilbloodydemon/netbeans-cakephp-bundle
